Package org.spongepowered.api.event.block.tileentity

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    BrewingStandBrewEvent
    An event when a BrewingStand freshly brews ItemStacks into new potions.
    BrewingStandEvent
    An event related to a BrewingStand.
    FurnaceConsumeFuelEvent
    An event when a Furnace consumes an ItemStack as fuel.
    FurnaceEvent
    Represents an event that affects a tile entity with a Furnace data.
    FurnaceSmeltItemEvent
    An event that occurs when a Furnace smelt an item.
    SignChangeEvent
    An event when a Sign is changed.
    SignEvent
    An event that is associated with a Sign.
    TileEntityChangeEvent
    Represents events where the DataManipulator of the TileEntity may change from the resolution of the event.
    TileEntityEvent
    An event that involves a TileEntity.
